269
00:18:54.550 --> 00:18:57.093
That's the problem with hospitals. sir.
There's no place to get singles.

270
00:18:58.554 --> 00:19:00.680
This is fun. Babies are fun.

271
00:19:00.681 --> 00:19:02.892
